verbose_text: Direct comparison of phospo-Ulk, phospho-Beclin, phospho-PI3-K / Vps34, and p62 levels in hippocampal extracts showed increased constitutive autophagy in Asm deficient mice and decreased autophagy in Asm-transgenic mice compared to wt mice.
evidence: p62 levels in hippocampal extracts showed increased constitutive autophagy in Asm-deficient mice and decreased autophagy
